snippet.textDisplay:
Being a Bengali, born and brought up in a Hindu family in India, we get so brainwashed that Bangladesh is this or that. But, in reality, those are just lies and by doing so, we, Indian Bengalis, have been washed off our Bengali identity by blatant Islamphobia and racism towards Bangladeshis. (Here Bangladeshi is meant by all the citizen of Bangladesh)

Bengalis of Bangladesh are really carrying forward the Bengali civilization and culture. Also they are doing good in every other sphere. Kudos! মাশাল্লাহ! আরো এগিয়ে চলো।❤️
